，對後來興起而又漸成主流嘅本土派嚟講，蘋果日報有少少愚鈍亦不足為奇，咁當然宜家睇返轉頭好多傳統泛民亦只係牛皮燈籠），分裂民主陣營，再將敵人逐一消滅"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T02:12:23.000Z","msg":"唔怪之得上次直播話大紀元唔容易<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我仲諗緊係咪最近比人搞，除咗呢單應該背後都比人搞"},{"pid":"4593032bf1c1e5ed5da142c22e166ef68a79556b","tid":2263292,"uid":156335,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e84833a63ef82bd42b2c1e4909a463f6b05e598b","tid":2263292,"uid":26770,"like":284,"dislike":3,"score":281,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T19:16:05.000Z","msg":"大紀元經常派人去示威現場影警暴<br />\n仲一再踢爆香港警魔強姦,酷刑<br />\n<br />\n結果遭香港政府報復<br />\n證明大紀元無講錯, 香港警魔就係反人類畜牲"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T02:13:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />全世界警察都會拎香港黑警比較，因為黑警最黑"},{"pid":"39bd90f42c022e444caa948935ddd00b4e2dcbaa","tid":2263292,"uid":73269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T02:13:49.000Z","msg":"大要人，subacribe and like"},{"pid":"ea1295271285475f118dbbdd3ce28abbc2bf1471","tid":2263292,"uid":290314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T02:14:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a3e3dce2cc612684f84ae979f1cf73d0ffc59aa","tid":2263292,"uid":202096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T02:15:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bfaaaa943a9058c06e521e690294da185376770b","tid":2263292,"uid":72262,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"b0ab6469b11cedc5ab8c6593d1755c19acdce862","tid":2263292,"uid":51225,"like":2,"dislike":17,"score":-15,"quote":{"pid":"01a0dc48835028c9da700b5e6de1794b4de9929b","tid":2263292,"uid":226955,"like":245,"dislike":9,"score":236,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T19:16:05.000Z","msg":"冇錯，大紀元的確係講緊真話，袁弓夷成日都喺佢地度講嘢<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5nvyNJq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https:/